Package: AzureGraph
Title: Interface to 'Azure Active Directory Graph'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hong", "Ooi", , "hongooi@microsoft.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Microsoft", role="cph")
    )
Description: A simple R interface to the 'Azure Active Directory Graph' REST API. It currently includes functionality to create and delete registered apps and service principals.
URL: https://github.com/cloudyr/AzureGraph
BugReports: https://github.com/cloudyr/AzureGraph/issues
